UML:TaggedValue.value: Goal : Execute Journey Transfer assistance Get journey real time information Check-in/check-out (for ticketing purpose) Emergency call Assistance call Provide social travel information (traffic information, disruption of service,...) Trigger: Traveler request a transfer assistance Primary actor: Traveler Pre-conditions: Traveler is en-route for a multi-modal trip and has to make a transfer between 2 transport means Post-conditions: Traveler has succeeded in accessing the following transport mean.
